<T extends AugmentedAnyModelType>(props: {
  item: T;
  backendAsset?: BackendAsset;
  hideDownloadLink?: boolean;
  className?: string;
}) => {
  const { backendAsset, item, hideDownloadLink, className } = props;

  return backendAsset ? (
    <AssetView
      asset={backendAsset}
      projectRelativeReferencingFilePath={item.projectRelativePath}
      hideDownloadLink={hideDownloadLink}
      className={className}
    />
  ) : null;
}
name: ModelItemAssetView
